<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Chosen Ones - Helping Families</title>
    <style>
        /* Color Palette */
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #1E2A47; /* Dark Purple */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #FF0000; /* Bright Red */
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #C3FF83; /* Lime Green */
        }

        header a {
            color: #C3FF83;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .services {
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #1E2A47; /* Dark Purple */
            text-align: center;
        }

        .services h2 {
            color: #FF0000; /* Bright Red */
            font-size: 2.2em;
        }

        .service {
            background-color: #333;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .service h3 {
            color: #C3FF83; /* Lime Green */
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }

        .service p {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .contact-form {
            background-color: #1E2A47; /* Dark Purple */
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .contact-form h2 {
            color: #FF0000; /* Bright Red */
            font-size: 2.2em;
        }

        .contact-form input, .contact-form select, .contact-form textarea {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #C3FF83;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .contact-form button {
            background-color: #C3FF83;
            color: #1E2A47; /* Dark Purple */
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .contact-form button:hover {
            background-color: #FF0000; /* Bright Red */
            color: white;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #1E2A47;
            color: #C3FF83;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>The Chosen Ones</h1>
    <p>Helping Families, One Day at a Time</p>
</header>

<section class="intro">
    <p><strong>Scarlett Kelly, Founder & Family Advocate</strong></p>
    <p>Our mission is simple: helping as many families as possible, one day at a time. You’ve told us that you need support—and that’s exactly what we’re here for. Whether you're navigating a challenging situation or just need guidance to move forward, we're here to provide the resources, support, and care that make a real difference in your lives.</p>
</section>

<section class="services">
    <h2>Our Services: Tailored for Families Like Yours</h2>

    <div class="service">
        <h3>"Our Ideas and Beyond" (1.5-Hour Consultation)</h3>
        <p>Looking for guidance on how to get started? This 1.5-hour consultation is perfect for families looking to navigate social systems, brainstorm new strategies, or simply get the ball rolling with fresh ideas. We’ll support you with practical steps and actionable solutions that will empower you to take control of your family’s journey.</p>
        <p><strong>Cost:</strong> $350 per session</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service">
        <h3>"Thinking Outside the Box" (A One-Time Plan to Overcome Challenges)</h3>
        <p>This service is for families in need of a focused, powerful plan for change. Whether you’re launching a new initiative at home, seeking community resources, or need a roadmap for your family's success, we’ll work with you to develop a strategy that makes a lasting impact.</p>
        <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Starting at $2,500 per campaign</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service">
        <h3>"We Come to You Directly" (Long-Term Partnership)</h3>
        <p>We’re not just consultants; we become a part of your family. This ongoing partnership means we are there to support you through the ups and downs, providing social services and guidance throughout the year. With a strong, steady approach, we help ensure your family thrives with tailored strategies for consistent growth and success.</p>
        <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Starting at $5,500 per month</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-form">
    <h2>Contact Us—Join Our Family</h2>
    <p>We’d love to hear from you and learn more about how we can help. Please take a moment to share a little about your needs below, or feel free to email us directly at <a href="mailto:scarlett.k18@gmail.com">scarlett.k18@gmail.com</a>. We look forward to connecting with you!</p>

    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/maykbjyo" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required><br>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required><br>
        <select name="service" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>Select Service</option>
            <option value="consultation">Our Ideas and Beyond</option>
            <option value="campaign">Thinking Outside the Box</option>
            <option value="partnership">We Come to You Directly</option>
        </select><br>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea><br>
        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
    </form>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>Thank you for reaching out! We’ll get back to you within 1-3 business days. Looking forward to connecting with you!</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
